text: The Kazakhstan national under-19 football team represents Kazakhstan in youth international football. They have qualified for the FIFA U-20 World Cup once in 1999 where they exited in the group stage without a win. ==FIFA U-20 World Cup== FIFA U-20 World Cup record Year Result 1977 Part of the Part of
